sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/SDK
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server
    participant DB as MariaDB
    participant ARGO as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant K8S as Kubernetes API
    participant POD as Pipeline Step Pod
    participant MINIO as Minio/S3
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata Envoy
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,PA: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission
    User->>+API: Submit Pipeline (HTTPS:8888, TLS 1.2+, Bearer Token)
    API->>+DB: Store Pipeline Metadata (MySQL:3306, TLS 1.2+, Password)
    DB-->>-API: Confirm
    API->>+ARGO: Create Workflow (HTTP:8080, ServiceAccount)
    ARGO->>+K8S: Create Workflow Resource (HTTPS:6443, TLS 1.3, SA)
    K8S-->>-ARGO: Confirm
    ARGO-->>-API: Workflow Created
    API-->>-User: Pipeline Submitted

    Note over ARGO,PA: Flow 2: Workflow Execution
    ARGO->>+K8S: Create Pipeline Step Pod (HTTPS:6443, TLS 1.3, SA)
    K8S-->>-ARGO: Pod Created
    POD->>+MINIO: Store/Retrieve Artifacts (HTTP:9000, TLS 1.2+, Access Key)
    MINIO-->>-POD: Artifact Data
    POD->>+MLMD: Track Lineage (gRPC:9090, mTLS, Client Cert)
    MLMD-->>-POD: Metadata Recorded
    PA->>+DB: Persist Workflow Metadata (MySQL:3306, TLS 1.2+, Password)
    DB-->>-PA: Confirm

    Note over POD,User: Flow 3: Artifact Storage
    POD->>+MINIO: Upload Artifact (HTTPS:9000 or 443, TLS 1.2+, Access Key)
    MINIO-->>-POD: Confirm
    API->>+MINIO: Generate Signed URL (HTTPS:9000 or 443, TLS 1.2+, Access Key)
    MINIO-->>-API: Signed URL
    User->>+MINIO: Download Artifact via Signed URL (HTTPS, TLS 1.2+)
    MINIO-->>-User: Artifact Data
